                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path d="M7 4V2a1 1 0 0 1 2 0v2h6V2a1 1 0 0 1 2 0v2h1a3 3 0 0 1 3 3v12a3 3 0 0 1-3 3H6a3 3 0 0 1-3-3V7a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h1z"/>
                        </svg>
                        Shopping Cart
                    </h3>
                    
